Except in the movies. On the other he is free with insulting references to the European Commission, whenever it is necessary to appeal to an audience of Euro-sceptics. Major's father, and therefore by extension John Major himself, can be all things to all people. A farmer for Farmers Weekly, a Pittsburgh steelworker for the American audience . I recall that he made a great hit by recounting that his father had been a steelworker in the city. My father was a farmer. Do not protest that the urban John Major could not identify with a gardener. 